CRAZY: M.O.M. augmented warrior, power at the cost of sanity

The Crazy is a warrior who has undergone Mind Over Matter (M.O.M.)
cybernetic implantation: metal spikes driven into the brain that unlock
psionic energy at the cost of sanity. Crazies are among the most
physically dangerous characters in the game, but they are unstable and
prone to erratic behavior.

Crazies gain ISP (psionic power) from their implants and combine this
with the physical enhancements of an elite soldier. They suffer random
psychotic episodes as a side effect of the procedure.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: IQ 9, PS 10, PE 10.
  ISP: Starting ISP pool from M.O.M. implants.
  Equipment: M.O.M. implants (fitted), light body armor, two ranged
    weapons, vibro-knife, and a personal sidearm.

